$ Line discipline

The line discipline glues the upper and the lower layer of the → Linux/terminal-subsystem[terminal subsystem] together. See especially the `struct tty_ldics_ops` (→ Linux/kernel/source/include/linux/tty_ldisc_h).
  
sa:
  → Linux/kernel/source/drivers/char/n_tty_c (Implementation of the default *line discipline*).
